6. Token and Tokenization
Token:
‚Ä¢	A collection of rules stored in a smart contract
‚Ä¢	Represents a digital asset
‚Ä¢	Associated with a blockchain address
Tokenization:
The process of converting tangible and intangible assets into blockchain tokens.
Applications:
‚Ä¢	Real Estate
‚Ä¢	Stocks
‚Ä¢	Art & Digital Assets
