7. Features of Blockchain
1.	Transparency
o	Transactions visible through public ledger
2.	Immutability
o	Data cannot be altered; only appended
3.	High Availability
o	Distributed and peer-to-peer architecture
4.	Security
o	Cryptographically protected
5.	Anonymity
o	Users can remain pseudonymous
