8. Database vs Blockchain
Database	Blockchain
Centralized	Decentralized
Supports CRUD operations	Append-only
Data can be modified	Data is immutable
Difficult to scale	High scalability
Admin controls data	No single authority
Data stored directly	Hashes of data stored
