________________________________________
Key Points to Remember (Exam Ready)
‚Ä¢	Validator selection is random but stake-weighted.
‚Ä¢	Minimum stake required: 32 ETH.
‚Ä¢	Rewards depend on:
o	Amount of ETH staked
o	Validator uptime and honest participation
‚Ä¢	Misbehavior leads to slashing, ensuring network security.
________________________________________
Summary
In Ethereum PoS, validators earn rewards for proposing and attesting blocks, while dishonest or inactive validators are penalized through slashing.


